stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Monitoring : AlertEngine starts

    Monitoring --> AlertRaised : threshold crossed\n(after hours / too long)
    AlertRaised --> Monitoring : condition clears\n(device turned off)

    AlertRaised --> IncidentOpen : IncidentAggregator\ngroups room alerts
    IncidentOpen --> IncidentResolved : all room alerts\nclear (room OFF)
    IncidentResolved --> [*]

    note right of AlertRaised
        Alert types:
        • device_on_after_hours (medium)
        • room_on_after_hours (high)
        • room_on_too_long (high)
    end note
